metadata.name: After Midnight
metadata.description:
As the Zombie looked to gather his scattered bits from the earth, he could make no sense of which parts came first- was he a man now undead? Or a man simply dying? With the temptations after midnight looming- he questions- was he ever truly alive? 

[Artwork (.png)](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmX3QTy4Fb5eesJNbi3UMWREUcs3e8Uet416UpUBdTpXpj)

[Lyrics (.png)](https://gateway.pinata.cloud/ipfs/QmRCqPuqH6pu464jQRaJ9DsYeeU6BFvj74Q65HhVLbErdg)
